text: * Fyi - I made a blunder w the recipe. The brown/white sugar blend was meant to be mixed with the yolks. And the egg whites should have been beaten to stiff peaks with only white sugar. But my Mom was talking to me & I poured the brown sugar in with the egg whites and realised it was too late. Didn’t want to throw out the whites so I just whisked it up anyway. It whisked up fine but wasn’t as firm even after 10 minutes because of the density of the brown sugar. There was a bit of water seeping out after I set it aside for a while. But this didn’t impact the end product 🤷🏻‍♀️*
